spec_data.Name: python2-MultipartPostHandler2
spec_data.Description:
This is MultipartPostHandler plus a fix for UTF-8 systems.
Enables the use of multipart/form-data for posting forms.

spec_data.Summary: A handler for urllib2 to enable multipart form uploading
